Description: Beautiful Kate Spade New York Charm City Ostrich Handbag in the "Provence" style, with spiffy flat bow in front. (Please forgive the photos...I didn't want to remove the protective foam. Please see the last photo for a photo *SAMPLE* of the bag without foam in *A DIFFERENT COLOR.*) The color is a summery "Strawberry Daiquiri," which looks just like it sounds -- a bright pink, tempered with a touch of salmon -- really striking, and at the moment, I don't see any others on E-Bay in this colorway! The bag can be carried by the handles, or with a strap (very long -- I'd say it would work best as a cross-body style. It's all wound up, though, so I can't give you the exact length. It is detachable.) Height (excluding handle): 8", Width: 11", Depth: 5" at widest point (3" at most narrow) Drop: (top of handle, to top of bag): 5" Great size -- not too big, but not too small -- just right for holding your essentials, and then some! Center zip pocket, and two open pockets on either side. Signature Kate Spade beige lining. Goldtone hardware and Kate Spade New You plate. Retailed for $325 (originally $428!) I hate to part with this one, but I haven't used it yet, so time for it to move on to another loving home. Feel free to message me with any further questions, and I'm happy to help you as best I can.
Title: NWT Kate Spade Charm City Provence Ostrich Handbag Strawberry Daiquiri
